   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Code: GPT-2 Tokenizer Se Dekhna\n",
    "\n",
    "Ab OpenAI ke **GPT-2** model ka tokenizer dekhte hainà¥¤ Yeh Language Models ki duniya mein bahut famous haià¥¤ Yeh thoda alag tarika use karta hai jisko Byte Pair Encoding (BPE) kehte hain, aur yeh spaces ko bhi words ka part treat karta haià¥¤"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "colab": {
     "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
     "height": 284
    },
    "executionInfo": null,
    "outputs": [],
    "source": [
     "# show_tokens function ko hamara text aur GPT-2 tokenizer ka naam do.\n",
     "# \"gpt2\" OpenAI ka bahut popular Language Model hai.\n",
     "# Iska tokenizer Byte Pair Encoding (BPE) use karta hai (yeh tokenization strategy ka ek naam hai).\n",
     "# Iska ek khas baat hai ki yeh spaces ko word ka part treat karta hai (dekhna output mein).\n",
     "show_tokens(text, \"gpt2\")\n",
     "\n",
     "# Output dekho! Yeh tokenizer BERT se alag hai:\n",
     "# - Sabse pehle, yeh word ke aage space ko bhi ek token bana deta hai (bahut se tokens space \" \" se shuru ho rahe hain).\n",
     "# - CAPITALIZATION ab ek saath hai, BERT cased jaisa bahut saare tukdon mein nahi toot raha.\n",
     "# - Special characters/emojis (ðŸŽµ, é¸Ÿ) ke liye yahan ek alag hi symbol ï¿½ aa raha hai (Unicode replacement character).\n",
     "# - Tabs (multiple spaces) bhi multiple space tokens mein toot rahe hain, na ki '\\t' jaisa BERT mein.\n",
     "# Har tokenizer ka apna signature style hai! GPT-2 ka space handling BERT se alag hai, aur special chars handling bhi."
    ]
   }
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Yeh Code Kya Karta Hai? ðŸ¤”**\n",
    "\n",
    "Yeh code hamare test `text` ko OpenAI ke GPT-2 model ke tokenizer se process karke dikhata hai. Socho yeh GPT-2 ke translator se text ko tod kar dekh rahe hainà¥¤ Yeh words ke aage space ko bhi ek alag token bana deta hai (output mein dekho, bahut saare tokens space se shuru ho rahe hain)à¥¤ Yeh bhi words ko tukdon mein todta hai par alag tarike se, aur special characters/emojis ke liye `ï¿½` jaisa token dikhata haià¥¤ Tabs (`    `) ko bhi spaces ke tokens mein tod deta hai. Is tokenizer mein BERT jaise `[CLS]` ya `[SEP]` special tokens nahi hote."
   ]
