    "**Yeh Code Kya Karta Hai? ðŸ¤”**\n",
    "\n",
    "Yeh code hamare `vector` variable ka `shape` print karta haià¥¤ Output `(768,)` (number vary ho sakta hai) dikhayega. Iska matlab hai ki hamara poora sentence ek single list of 768 numbers se represent ho raha haià¥¤ Socho yeh poore LEGO model ka ek final score hai! Contextualized embeddings se alag, yahan har token ka alag vector nahi hai, balki poore sentence ka ek consolidated vector haià¥¤ Yahi hain **Text Embeddings**à¥¤ In vectors ka use karke hum do sentences ya documents ki similarity measure kar sakte hain (jitne paas vectors, utna similar matlab)à¥¤"
   ]
