   "source": [
    "**Yeh Code Kya Karta Hai? ðŸ¤”**\n",
    "\n",
    "Yeh code `songs_df` DataFrame (hamari song details ki table) ka use karke `song_id` 2172 ke details (title aur artist) print karta hai. Socho tumne song ID ka code enter kiya aur table ne gaane ka naam aur artist bata diyaà¥¤ Kyunki humne `song_hash.txt` file ko load karte waqt song ID ko index banaya tha, hum `songs_df.loc[str(2172)]` se us song ki row easily nikal sakte hainà¥¤ Isse humein pata chalta hai ki hum kis original song ke liye recommendations dekh rahe hainà¥¤ Recommendations check karte waqt original item ki details pata hona accha hai!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
