    "Yeh code `print_recommendations` naam ka ek function banata haià¥¤ Socho yeh ek music recommender machine hai! Yeh function ek song ID input leta haià¥¤ Us ID ko string mein badal kar `model.wv.most_similar` se top 5 similar song IDs aur unke similarity scores dhundhta haià¥¤ Phir similar song IDs ki list extract karta haià¥¤ Iske baad, `songs_df.loc[]` ka use karke un 5 recommended song IDs ki details (title, artist) nikal kar ek DataFrame mein wapas karta haià¥¤ Yeh function hamara recommendation logic haià¥¤\n",
    "\n",
    "Jab hum `print_recommendations(2172)` call karte hain, toh yeh function song 2172 ke liye top 5 recommendations dhundh kar ek DataFrame mein dikhata hai. Pichhle step mein humne dekha tha ki song 2172 Metallica ka \"Fade To Black\" haià¥¤ Ab dekhte hain iske recommendations kya aate hain!"
