    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## ðŸ“š Seekhe Hue Shabd (Glossary)\n",
    "\n",
    "Chalo, jo naye aur important technical shabd humne is Chapter mein seekhe, unka matlab aur thoda simple explanation aur analogies dekh lete hain, taaki yeh sab yaad rahe! Socho yeh hamari AI dictionary hai!\n",
    "\n",
    "*   **Tokens:** Bhasha (text) ke chote chote tukde jinmein AI model input ko todta hai. Yeh poore shabd ho sakte hain (\"cat\"), shabdon ke hisse (`apolog`, `izing`), punctuation (`.`, `:`), ya special symbols/charactersà¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise building blocks ya LEGO pieces jinse poora sentence banta haià¥¤ Har token ek block hai!\n",
    "*   **Tokenization:** Woh process jismein Language Model ka tokenizer input text ko in chote chote **Tokens** mein todta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise koi complicated cheez ko chote chote parts mein divide karna usko study karne ya use karne ke liye, ya LEGO set ko uske pieces mein alag karna banane se pehleà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Tokenizer:** Woh tool ya software jo text ko tokens mein todta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Woh machine ya person jo tumhari bhasha ko AI ke LEGO pieces mein badalta haià¥¤\n",
    "*   **Token ID:** Har unique token ke liye ek special number. AI model tokens ko unke IDs se pehchanta hai aur numbers par kaam karta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise har LEGO piece ka apna ek unique number ya code ho jo uski pehchan haià¥¤ AI numbers (IDs) par kaam karta hai, text par nahià¥¤\n",
    "*   **Embeddings:** Tokens (ya poore sentences/documents) ko represent karne wali numbers ki list (jisko technical language mein **vector** kehte hain). Yeh numbers token/text ke \"matlab\" ya meaning ko capture karte hainà¥¤ **Analogy:** Har LEGO piece ka ek \"power level\" ya \"functionality score\" list, jo batata hai ki woh kis tarah ka piece hai aur kya kar sakta haià¥¤ Jin pieces ka kaam similar hai, unke scores paas paas hongeà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Embedding Size / Vector Dimension:** Ek embedding vector mein kitne numbers hain, uski lambaià¥¤ **Analogy:** Woh \"power level score card\" mein kitni entries hain (kitne alag alag tarah ke scores)à¥¤\n",
    "*   **Contextualized Embeddings:** Modern LLMs dwara banaye gaye embeddings jahan ek token ka meaning number uske aas paas ke shabdon (context) par depend karta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise \"bank\" shabd ka matlab meaning number list sentence ke hisaab se badal jayega - river bank wala bank ka number money bank wale bank se alag hogaà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Text Embeddings / Sentence Embeddings:** Ek single meaning number list (vector) jo poore sentence ya poore document ke combined matlab ko represent karta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise poore LEGO model ka ek overall score jo batata hai ki woh kis tarah ka model hai (car, building, etc.)à¥¤ Yeh do models ko compare karne ke kaam aata haià¥¤\n",
    "*   **Non-Contextual Embeddings:** Purane tarike ke embeddings jahan ek word ka meaning number hamesha same rehta hai, bhale hi woh kisi bhi context mein hoà¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise purani dictionary jismein har word ka ek hi entry ho, \"bank\" ka ek hi matlab ho numbers meinà¥¤ Word2Vec aur GloVe iske examples hainà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Word2Vec:** Non-Contextual Word Embeddings banane ka ek popular algorithm jo shabdon ke aas paas ke shabdon (context) ke hisaab se numbers deta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Jaise shabdon ki dosti ka score: jo shabd dost hain (aksar saath aate hain), unke numbers paas paas hongeà¥¤ Humne isko song recommendations ke liye use kiya!\n",
    "*   **GloVe:** Non-Contextual Word Embeddings banane ka ek aur popular algorithmà¥¤ Yeh World2Vec se thoda alag tarike se kaam karta hai par idea similar haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Dosti ka score calculate karne ka ek doosra tarikaà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Gensim:** Ek Python library jo Word Embeddings (jaise Word2Vec, GloVe) aur related text processing tasks ke liye tools deta haià¥¤ **Analogy:** Ek toolkit jismein Word Embeddings banane aur use karne ke saare auzaar hainà¥¤\n",
    "*   **Pandas:** Python mein data ko tables (DataFrames) mein organize karne ke liye ek bahut useful libraryà¥¤ **Analogy:** Ek smart spreadsheet table jismein songs ki IDs ke saath unke naam aur artist likhe hain, aur hum ID se jaldi dhundh sakte hainà¥¤\n",
    "*   **DataFrame (Pandas):** Pandas library mein table-like data structureà¥¤ Rows aur columns hote hainà¥¤ **Analogy:** Wahi smart spreadsheet table jiske baare mein abhi baat kià¥¤\n",
    "*   **GPU (Graphics Processing Unit):** Computer mein ek special chip jo bahut saari math calculations ek saath tez kar sakti haià¥¤ AI models ko train aur run karne ke liye bahut usefulà¥¤ **Analogy:** Ek Super Engine jo AI ke kaam ko Rocket ðŸš€ jaisa tez kar deta hai!\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "ðŸ’¡ **Picture Suggestion:** Yahan par ek image mein dictionary jaisi book dikha sakte ho, aur uske side mein ek graph jismein points (shabd) alag alag groups mein paas paas hon (jaise animals ka group, fruits ka group) aur un points ke paas numbers likhe honà¥¤ Isse Embeddings ka idea clear hogaà¥¤"
