    "## âœ… Summary: Kya Seekha Aur Aage Kya? ðŸŽ‰\n",
    "\n",
    "Waah! Aaj humne AI ke andar ke kuch bahut important aur interesting concepts ko explore kiyaà¥¤ Socho hum AI ke dimag mein jhaank kar aaye hain! Humne seekha:\n",
    "\n",
    "*   AI models hamari bhasha ko chote chote **Tokens** mein todte hain (using a **Tokenizer**), jaise sentence ko LEGO pieces mein todnaà¥¤ Har token ka ek **Token ID** hota hai, jo uska unique code haià¥¤\n",
    "*   Humne dekha ki alag alag models ke **Tokenizers** ek hi text ko alag alag tarike se handle karte hain (case, spaces, symbols), sabka apna apna style haià¥¤\n",
    "*   Humne seekha ki **Embeddings** kya hote hain - tokens ya text ko represent karne wale meaning numbers (vectors)à¥¤ Socho yeh har token ka 'matlab score card' haià¥¤\n",
    "*   Humne **Contextualized Embeddings** (jaise BERT/DeBERTa se) ko dekha, jahan meaning numbers shabd ke sentence mein use hone ke context ke hisaab se badalte hainà¥¤ \"Bank\" ka matlab badla, uska number badla!\n",
    "*   Humne **Text Embeddings** (Sentence-BERT se) ko dekha, jo poore sentence ya document ka ek single meaning number dete hain, do sentences ki similarity check karne ke liye perfectà¥¤\n",
    "*   Humne **Non-Contextual Embeddings** (jaise Word2Vec/GloVe) ko dekha, jo LLMs se pehle aate the aur jahan word ka embedding hamesha same rehta hai, bhale hi context kuch bhi hoà¥¤\n",
    "*   Aur sabse mazedaar baat, humne dekha ki kaise **embeddings** ka use karke hum real-world applications bana sakte hain, jaise song recommendations! ðŸŽ¶ Yeh dikhata hai ki meaning numbers kitne useful ho sakte hainà¥¤\n",
    "\n",
    "Yeh Chapter AI ke Language understanding ki foundation hai. Tokens aur Embeddings woh tarika hai jisse computer hamari baaton ko numerical roop deta hai jispar calculations ki ja sakein aur AI \"samajh\" sakeà¥¤\n",
